text: Peter Koprivnikar (born 2 July 1976) is a Slovenian archer. Koprivnikar competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics.Peter KoprivnikarPeter KOPRIVNIKAR ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian archers Category:Olympians for Slovenia
